'''Cut-the-knot'''是由Alexander Bogomolny维护的一个教育网站，专注于通俗地介绍各类数学话题。该网站已经获得20多个来自科学和教育出版方面的奖项，<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2006-01-18|url=http://www.cut-the-knot.org/awards.shtml|title=cut-the-knot's list of awards|archive-date=2006-09-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060928055611/http://www.cut-the-knot.org/awards.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>，包括[[科学美国人|科学美国人]]“网站奖”（2003年）<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2006-01-18|url=http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?articleID=00077DD8-59F2-1ECA-8E1C809EC588EF21|title=Scientific American 2003 Sci/Tech Web Awards: MATHEMATICS|archive-date=2006-03-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060316190022/http://www.scientificamerican.com/article.cfm?articleID=00077DD8-59F2-1ECA-8E1C809EC588EF21|dead-url=no}}</ref>，[[大不列颠百科全书|大不列颠百科全书]]“互联网向导奖”（Internet Guide Award）{{ref|awards}}，和[[科学_(期刊)|科学]]“网络观察奖”（NetWatch award）<ref>{{cite journal|volume=285|issue=5424|year=1999-07-02|journal=[[科学_(期刊)|''Science'' Magazine]]|title=SITE VISIT: Mathematical Wonders|url=http://www.sciencemag.org/content/vol285/issue5424/netwatch.dtl|access-date=2008-10-26|archive-date=2009-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208191643/http://www.sciencemag.org/content/vol285/issue5424/netwatch.dtl|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它的名字源于[[亚历山大大帝|亚历山大大帝]]解[[戈尔迪的结|戈尔迪的结]]（[[戈耳狄俄斯之结|Gordian knot]]）的传说。

Cut-the-knot宣称"Judging Mathematics by its pragmatic value is like judging symphonia by the weight of its score"，将该网站描述为"a resource that would help learn, if not math itself, then, at least, ways to appreciate its beauty."<ref>{{cite web|accessdate=2006-01-18|url=http://www.cut-the-knot.org/manifesto/index.shtml|title=Cut-the-knot's manifesto|archive-date=2006-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060419190305/http://www.cut-the-knot.org/manifesto/index.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>
该网站为老师、学生和家长以及为了教育、鼓励兴趣、刺激好奇心任何对数学感兴趣的人设计。许多数学理念做成了[[applet|applet]]程序演示。

